2.You are given an array arr of numbers. Return the sum of all the elements except the first and last elements.
Platform : GeeksForGeeks
SOURCE CODE : class Solution {
    int sumExceptFirstLast(int[] arr) {
      int sum=0;int n=arr.length;
      for(int i=1;i<n-1;i++){
          sum+=arr[i];
      }
      return sum;
    }
}
